{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1684-12_003", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Explications de la Galerie de Versailles]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", décembre 1684 [tome 14], p. 3-4, 27-28."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "EXPLICATION"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "DE LA GALERIE"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[2]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[3]", "text": "DE VERSAILLES."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "L’Allégorie est la maniere la plus ancienne d’exprimer les pensées par des caracteres. Les lettres n’ont esté en usage que longtemps apres que les Egyptiens eurent, par des figures, laissé à la Postérité les Mistéres de leur Religion, & les Loix de leur Etat. Les Poëtes depuis, sous des sens allégoriques, dans les Métamorphoses, & dans les Fables, nous ont donné les plus beaux préceptes, & les leçons les plus utiles de la Philosophie. [...]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Dans le second, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "a"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": " on reconnoist l’institution des Académies. Le Roy est accompagné de Minerve, qui tient un Plan de l’Observatoire. L’Académie Françoise porte un Câducée "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "b"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[3]", "text": " à la main. Elle est à la teste de ses Compagnes, pour lesquelles elle remercie le Prince de l’honneur de sa protection. [...]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[1]", "tag": "note", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[1]/text()[1]", "text": "a "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Du costé des Fenestres."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}], "attributes": {"resp": "author"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[2]", "tag": "note", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[2]/text()[1]", "text": "b "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Symbole de l’Eloquence."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}], "attributes": {"resp": "author"}}]}]}